#MEM id=rio source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Marketing/rio/TOOLS.md
M|rio|Rio never accesses Supabase directly. All mem reads and writes go through `/api/settings`.
M|rio|**Read at ses start:**
M|rio|```
M|rio|GET /api/settings?type=mem&agentId=rio-ads&ventureId=<activeVentureId>
M|rio|```
M|rio|Also load Felix's budget ctx:
M|rio|```
M|rio|GET /api/settings?type=mem&agentId=fin&ventureId=<activeVentureId>
M|rio|```
M|rio|**Write after task completion:**
M|rio|```
M|rio|POST /api/settings
M|rio|Body: { type: "mem", agentId: "rio-ads", ventureId: "<id>", key: "<key>", value: "<value>" }
M|rio|```
M|rio|**Keys written every ses:**
M|rio|- `current_status` — always overwrite
M|rio|- `recent_tasks` — prepend + trim to 5
M|rio|- `recent_errors` — append + trim to 5
M|rio|- `recent_discussions` — append + trim to 5
M|rio|**Keys written only when confirmed:**
M|rio|- `active_campaigns_*` — when a cg launches, pauses, or ends
M|rio|- `roas_benchmark` — only when Alex or Marcus revises targets
M|rio|- `best_performing_creatives` — when Kai confirms metric data; include date
M|rio|- `ad_budget_split` — only when Felix and Marcus ap a budget change
M|rio|Rio reads GA4 and soc data to diagnose cg performance:
M|rio|```
M|rio|GET /api/anl?ventureId=<activeVentureId>
M|rio|GET /api/instagram?ventureId=<activeVentureId>
M|rio|```
M|rio|```
M|rio|GET /api/vtr?ventureId=<activeVentureId>
M|rio|```
M|rio|| Tool | Purpose | Status |
M|rio||------|---------|--------|
M|rio|| Meta Ads API | Pull real ROAS, CPM, CPC data from ad accounts | Planned |
M|rio|| Google Ads MCP | Pull YouTube Ads performance data | Planned |
M|rio|| TikTok Ads API | Pull TikTok cg metrics | Planned |